/*
*  Package Operations:
* =======================
*  This package defines a WPF application that provides the GUI design to convert
*  and publish files matching specific patterns and regex present at a remote server.
*
*  Required Files:
* =======================
*  MainWindow.xaml MainWindow.xaml.cs
*
